title: Hillsong Church
label: Mobile
description: Hillsong Church is a church community app. where members of the church can submit prayer requests, praise reports, requests for help, volunteer opportunities, and community group memberships. Through the app, users can view church events and listen to live radio broadcasts.

title: SIPOLI
label: Mobile & Tablet
description: SIPOLI is a SIM-making psychotest application that allows users to submit SIM creations, SIM extensions, and other SIM-related items. The program also allows users to take the test, view submissions made in the past, and view the psychological test's results.
